===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|ojp|jpx-pro|*yoru}}.

Derived from ''yo<sub>1</sub>'' below, suffixed with an element ''ru'' of unclear meaning.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> Compare {{m|ojp|日||tr=pi<sub>1</sub>|[[day]]}} → {{m|ojp|晝||tr=pi<sub>1</sub>ru|[[daytime]]}}, which seems to use this same ''ru'' element.

Used as a standalone noun but not in compounds.

